data.description: This Liberty Home Builders property in the quiet community of Woodland Pines is a must see! The stunning home is situated in a corner lot offering a spacious backyard with a covered patio to build your backyard Oasis.  The home floor plan offers 4bdr 2.5 bath, high ceilings, slate tile backsplash, living and dining room with plenty of lighting, slate tile on stairs. Large Master Suite with bay window, double vanities, a vast walking closet. Large Game room and spacious bedrooms on the second floor. Ideal Location with easy access to Beltway 8 & 59 Intercontinental Airport, Hardy Toll Rd. Schedule your showing today.
